acceptance_criteria: "update-many and close-many are reachable as facets of update/close with identical semantics including dry-run parity and validate-close; delete and restore live under exactly one noun per the accepted ADR; old spellings alias-dispatch with hints; spelling-parity spec green; contracts, completions, docs, and MCP names regenerated."
